        <abstract>
            <para>We present here a database on the wet or submerged mosses collected in bogs and fens in Northwestern Italy in 2023 and 2024. We sampled five areas and collected 35 samples. The survey yielded a total of 17 species belonging to seven genera.</para>
        </abstract>
